{\b0 \cf1 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
In light of the dependency statutory scheme and federal due process principles, parental unfitness or neglectful conduct must be shown in order to assert dependency court jurisdiction over a child based on the parent\rquote s \u8220\'3finability to adequately supervise or protect the child.\u8221\'3f 
}
