{\ri30 \li30 
{\b0 \cf1 \f2 \ri30 \i0 \ql \fs20 \li30 
{\b0 \cf1 \f2 \ri30 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li30 
{\b0 \cf1 \f2 \ri30 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li30 
{\b0 \cf1 \f2 \ri30 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li30 
{\b0 \cf1 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
The California dependency system comports with federal due process requirements because the number and quality of the judicial findings that are necessary preconditions to termination of parental rights convey very powerfully to the fact finder the subjective certainty about parental unfitness and detriment required before the court may even consider ending the relationship between natural parent and child. 
}
