}\b0 \cf28 \f6 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 }}
{\b0 \cf1 \f6 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 providing for jurisdiction based on the \u8220\'3finability of the parent or guardian to provide regular care for the child due to the parent\rquote s or guardian\rquote s mental illness, developmental disability, or substance abuse.\u8221\'3f (
}
